<p><a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/473843a6h833b6ac41274" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/473843a6h833b6ac41274&amp;690" /></A><br />

